OL,3,CNew service cuts waiting times for
OL,4,Cwomb cancer appointments by two months
OL,6,FBeatriz told ITV News' Ben McGrail how
OL,7,Fshe was seen within days of referring
OL,8,Fherself.
OL,10,FA new service making it easier for
OL,11,Fpatients to get checked for a common
OL,12,Ftype of cancer has cut waiting times
OL,13,Ffor a diagnosis by more than eight
OL,14,Fweeks.
OL,16,FThe service, run by Somerset NHS
OL,17,FFoundation Trust, allows those
OL,18,Fdisplaying symptoms of cancer of the
OL,19,Flining of the womb to make a self-
OL,20,Freferral without having to visit their
OL,21,FGP.
