OL,3,CNew service cuts waiting times for
OL,4,Cwomb cancer appointments by two months
OL,6,FIt has seen a huge cut in the average
OL,7,Fwaiting time from 63 days to four and
OL,8,Fthe service has already seen more than
OL,9,F150 patients refer themselves since
OL,10,Fits launch in September 2023.
OL,12,FBeatriz Velasco is one of those
OL,13,Fpatients. After noticing concerning
OL,14,Fsymptoms she was seen within days of
OL,15,Freferring herself and was given
OL,16,Freassurance on the spot.
OL,18,FShe said: "I called the service on the
OL,19,FFriday morning and I was given an
OL,20,Fappointment for the next Thursday.
