OL,3,CNew service cuts waiting times for
OL,4,Cwomb cancer appointments by two months
OL,6,F"It takes the anxiety away because you
OL,7,Fdon't want to be weeks and weeks
OL,8,Fwaiting or thinking about that there
OL,9,Fcould be something bad. So I was given
OL,10,Fthat reassurance very quickly and I
OL,11,Ffound the whole service very positive."
OL,13,FIt would normally take three
OL,14,Fappointments to get to where Beatriz
OL,15,Fdid - seeing a GP, going for an
OL,16,Fultrasound then an outpatient
OL,17,Fappointment, usually at one of the
OL,18,Fmajor hospitals.
