OL,3,CNew service cuts waiting times for
OL,4,Cwomb cancer appointments by two months
OL,6,FInstead, a "one stop" at community
OL,7,Fhospitals around Somerset has cut out
OL,8,Fthe middleman, reducing average waits
OL,9,Fby two months. The service is believed
OL,10,Fto be a UK first.
OL,12,FNurse practitioner Heather Fryer said:
OL,13,F"When they come in they will initially
OL,14,Fgo off to have a pelvic ultrasound
OL,15,Fscan, that's looking at the uterus, in
OL,16,Fparticular.
