OL,3,CNew service cuts waiting times for
OL,4,Cwomb cancer appointments by two months
OL,6,F"That will get 'hot reported' and
OL,7,Fthey'll come over and see clinicians
OL,8,Fand then depending on the result of
OL,9,Fthe scan it'll determine what further
OL,10,Finvestigations are needed.
OL,12,F"For the majority of ladies they just
OL,13,Fneed a pelvic examination and then
OL,14,Fthey can be reassured and discharged
OL,15,Fhome but for some other ladies they'll
OL,16,Fneed some further tests and then other
OL,17,Fladies perhaps will need further
OL,18,Finvestigations within secondary care."
