OL,3,CNew service cuts waiting times for
OL,4,Cwomb cancer appointments by two months
OL,6,FConsultant gynaecological oncologist
OL,7,FDavid Milliken said: "We know that we
OL,8,Fweren't meeting the targets for
OL,9,Flooking after patients well enough and
OL,10,Ftherefore something had to change.
OL,12,F"Necessity being the mother of
OL,13,Finvention, this is what we've done and
OL,14,Fthankfully in this instance it seems
OL,15,Fto be working well. It's not a one
OL,16,Fsize fits all - I think this is a
OL,17,Fsolution for our particular patient
OL,18,Fpopulation in a rural county like
OL,19,FSomerset.
